532025,115,2327,62,95,1,274,29,Tasmiṃ khaṇe sakko manussalokaṃ olokento mahāsattassa mātukucchito nikkhamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ imaṃ buddhaṅkuraṃ sadevake loke pākaṭaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti mahāsattassa mātukucchito nikkhantakkhaṇe adissamānakāyena gantvā tassa hatthe ekaṃ osadhaghaṭikaṃ ṭhapetvā sakaṭṭhānameva gato. 
532026,115,2327,96,101,1,33,5,Mahāsatto taṃ muṭṭhiṃ katvā gaṇhi. 
532027,115,2327,102,115,1,110,12,"Tasmiṃ pana mātukucchito nikkhante mātu appamattakampi dukkhaṃ nāhosi, dhamakaraṇato udakamiva sukhena nikkhami. "
532028,115,2328,2,18,1,63,11,"Sā tassa hatthe osadhaghaṭikaṃ disvā‘‘ tāta, kiṃ te laddhan’’ ti āha."
532029,115,2328,19,31,1,47,7,"‘‘ Osadhaṃ, ammā’’ ti dibbosadhaṃ mātu hatthe ṭhapesi. "
532030,115,2328,32,50,1,80,13,"Ṭhapetvā ca pana‘‘ amma, idaṃ osadhaṃ yena kenaci ābādhena ābādhikānaṃ dethā’’ ti āha. "
532031,115,2328,51,55,1,46,4,Sā tuṭṭhapahaṭṭhā sirivaḍḍhanaseṭṭhino ārocesi. 
