532033,115,2328,62,98,1,244,29,"So tuṭṭhapahaṭṭho hutvā‘‘ ayaṃ mātukucchito jāyamāno osadhaṃ gahetvā āgato, jātakkhaṇeyeva mātarā saddhiṃ kathesi, evarūpena puññavatā dinnaṃ osadhaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā taṃ osadhaṃ gahetvā nisadāyaṃ ghaṃsitvā thokaṃ nalāṭe makkhesi. "
