532349,115,2368,52,59,1,43,6,So attano yuttāsanaṃ ñatvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
532350,115,2368,60,100,1,334,34,"Mahāsattopi alaṅkatapaṭiyatto dārakasahassaparivuto alaṅkatarathe nisīditvā nagaraṃ pavisanto parikhāpiṭṭhe caramānaṃ ekaṃ gadrabhaṃ disvā thāmasampanne māṇave pesesi‘‘ ambho, etaṃ gadrabhaṃ anubandhitvā yathā saddaṃ na karoti, evamassa mukhabandhanaṃ katvā kilañjena veṭhetvā tasmiṃ ekenattharaṇena paṭicchādetvā aṃsenādāya āgacchathā’’ ti. "
532351,115,2368,101,104,1,16,3,Te tathā kariṃsu. 
