532393,115,2376,76,105,1,139,21,"‘‘ Gahapati, tvaṃ ito paṭṭhāya etasmiṃ nirālayo hohi, ayaṃ ajjatagge mama putto, ahaṃ mama puttaṃ posetuṃ sakkhissāmi, gaccha tvan’’ ti taṃ uyyojesi. "
532394,115,2376,106,126,1,109,15,"So rājānaṃ vanditvā paṇḍitaṃ āliṅgitvā ure nipajjāpetvā sīse cumbitvā‘‘ tāta, appamatto hohī’’ ti ovādamassa adāsi. "
