532437,115,2381,222,248,1,117,20,"Rājā tassa taṃ kiriyaṃ oloketvā‘‘ paṇḍita, esa pubbe viya ajja na otarati, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti pucchanto imaṃ gāthamāha–"
