532441,115,2384,18,25,1,51,6,Kena {thaddho}ti kena kāraṇena thaddhabhāvaṃ āpannoti. 
532442,115,2385,2,28,1,170,21,"Paṇḍito tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ mahārāja, uposathe māghāte maṃsaṃ alabhantena rājapurisena gīvāya baddhaṃ aḍḍhamāsakaṃ nissāya tassa mānena bhavitabban’’ ti ñatvā imaṃ gāthamāha–"
