532447,115,2388,18,42,1,161,20,Rājā taṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ kañci apucchitvāva sabbaññubuddhena viya paṇḍitena kakaṇṭakassa ajjhāsayo ñāto’’ ti ativiya pasīditvā paṇḍitassa catūsu dvāresu suṅkaṃ dāpesi. 
532448,115,2388,43,49,1,49,6,Kakaṇṭakassa pana kujjhitvā vattaṃ hāretuṃ ārabhi. 
532449,115,2388,50,62,1,47,8,Paṇḍito pana‘‘ mā hārehi mahārājā’’ ti taṃ nivāresi. 
532450,115,2389,2,4,1,23,2,Kakaṇṭakapañho niṭṭhito. 
532451,115,2390,2,2,1,18,1,Sirikāḷakaṇṇipañho 
532452,115,2391,2,16,1,124,13,Atheko mithilavāsī piṅguttaro nāma māṇavo takkasilaṃ gantvā disāpāmokkhācariyassa santike sippaṃ sikkhanto khippameva sikkhi. 
532453,115,2391,17,28,1,49,7,So anuyogaṃ datvā‘‘ gacchāmahan’’ ti ācariyaṃ āpucchi. 
532454,115,2391,29,57,1,164,21,"Tasmiṃ pana kule‘‘ sace vayappattā dhītā hoti, jeṭṭhantevāsikassa dātabbā’’ ti vattaṃva, tasmā tassa ācariyassa vayappattā ekā dhītā atthi, sā abhirūpā devaccharāpaṭibhāgā. "
532455,115,2391,58,77,1,68,12,"Atha naṃ ācariyo‘‘ dhītaraṃ te, tāta, dassāmi, taṃ ādāya gamissasī’’ ti āha. "
532456,115,2391,78,87,1,57,8,"So pana māṇavo dubbhago kāḷakaṇṇī, kumārikā pana mahāpuññā. "
532457,115,2391,88,94,1,34,6,Tassa taṃ disvā cittaṃ na allīyati. 
532458,115,2391,95,108,1,66,9,So taṃ arocentopi‘‘ ācariyassa vacanaṃ na bhindissāmī’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
532459,115,2391,109,113,1,28,4,Ācariyo dhītaraṃ tassa adāsi. 
532460,115,2391,114,129,1,151,15,So rattibhāge alaṅkatasirisayane nipanno tāya āgantvā sayanaṃ abhiruḷhamattāya aṭṭīyamāno harāyamāno jigucchamāno pakampamāno otaritvā bhūmiyaṃ nipajji. 
532461,115,2391,130,141,1,71,10,"Sāpi otaritvā tassa santikaṃ gantvā nipajji, so uṭṭhāya sayanaṃ abhiruhi. "
532462,115,2391,142,153,1,67,10,"Sāpi puna sayanaṃ abhiruhi, so puna sayanā otaritvā bhūmiyaṃ nipajji. "
532463,115,2391,154,160,1,39,6,Kāḷakaṇṇī nāma siriyā saddhiṃ na sameti. 
532464,115,2391,161,168,1,44,6,"Kumārikā sayaneyeva nipajji, so bhūmiyaṃ sayi. "
532465,115,2392,2,14,1,102,11,"Evaṃ sattāhaṃ vītināmetvā taṃ ādāya ācariyaṃ vanditvā nikkhami, antarāmagge ālāpasallāpamattampi natthi. "
532466,115,2392,15,19,1,38,4,Anicchamānāva ubhopi mithilaṃ sampattā. 
532467,115,2392,20,33,1,112,13,Atha piṅguttaro nagarā avidūre phalasampannaṃ udumbararukkhaṃ disvā khudāya pīḷito taṃ abhiruhitvā phalāni khādi. 
532468,115,2392,34,49,1,73,10,"Sāpi chātajjhattā rukkhamūlaṃ gantvā‘‘ sāmi, mayhampi phalāni pātethā’’ ti āha. "
532469,115,2392,50,58,1,52,7,"Kiṃ tava hatthapādā natthi, sayaṃ abhiruhitvā khādāti. "
532470,115,2392,59,62,1,20,3,Sā abhiruhitvā khādi. 
532471,115,2392,63,83,1,116,14,So tassā abhiruḷhabhāvaṃ ñatvā khippaṃ otaritvā rukkhaṃ kaṇṭakehi parikkhipitvā‘‘ muttomhi kāḷakaṇṇiyā’’ ti vatvā palāyi. 
532472,115,2392,84,89,1,39,5,Sāpi otarituṃ asakkontī tattheva nisīdi. 
532473,115,2392,90,112,1,148,17,"Atha rājā uyyāne kīḷitvā hatthikkhandhe nisinno sāyanhasamaye nagaraṃ pavisanto taṃ disvā paṭibaddhacitto hutvā‘‘ sapariggahā, apariggahā’’ ti pucchāpesi. "
532474,115,2392,113,135,1,88,15,"Sāpi‘‘ atthi me, sāmi, kuladattiko pati, so pana maṃ idha nisīdāpetvā chaḍḍetvā palāto’’ ti āha. "
532475,115,2392,136,141,1,32,5,Amacco taṃ kāraṇaṃ rañño ārocesi. 
532476,115,2392,142,161,1,134,15,Rājā‘‘ asāmikabhaṇḍaṃ nāma rañño pāpuṇātī’’ ti taṃ otāretvā hatthikkhandhaṃ āropetvā nivesanaṃ netvā abhisiñcitvā aggamahesiṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. 
532477,115,2392,162,167,1,26,5,Sā tassa piyā ahosi manāpā. 
532478,115,2392,168,178,1,63,6,Udumbararukkhe laddhattā‘‘ udumbaradevī’’ tvevassā nāmaṃ sañjāniṃsu. 
532479,115,2393,2,9,1,78,6,Athekadivasaṃ rañño uyyānagamanatthāya dvāragāmavāsikehi maggaṃ paṭijaggāpesuṃ. 
532480,115,2393,10,18,1,69,8,Piṅguttaropi bhatiṃ karonto kacchaṃ bandhitvā kuddālena maggaṃ tacchi. 
532481,115,2393,19,27,1,72,8,Magge aniṭṭhiteyeva rājā udumbaradeviyā saddhiṃ rathe nisīditvā nikkhami. 
532482,115,2393,28,47,1,116,15,Udumbaradevī kāḷakaṇṇiṃ maggaṃ tacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ evarūpaṃ siriṃ dhāretuṃ nāsakkhi ayaṃ kāḷakaṇṇī’’ ti taṃ olokentī hasi. 
532483,115,2393,48,60,1,51,8,Rājā hasamānaṃ disvā kujjhitvā‘‘ kasmā hasī’’ ti pucchi. 
532484,115,2393,61,92,1,198,24,"Deva, ayaṃ maggatacchako puriso mayhaṃ porāṇakasāmiko, esa maṃ udumbararukkhaṃ āropetvā kaṇṭakehi parikkhipitvā gato, imāhaṃ oloketvā‘‘ evarūpaṃ siriṃ dhāretuṃ nāsakkhi kāḷakaṇṇī ayan’’ ti cintetvā hasinti. "
532485,115,2393,93,115,1,108,16,"Rājā‘‘ tvaṃ musāvādaṃ kathesi, aññaṃ kañci purisaṃ disvā tayā hasitaṃ bhavissati, taṃ māressāmī’’ ti asiṃ aggahesi. "
532486,115,2393,116,129,1,49,8,"Sā bhayappattā‘‘ deva, paṇḍite tāva pucchathā’’ ti āha. "
