532504,115,2402,2,4,1,27,2,Sirikāḷakaṇṇipañho niṭṭhito. 
532505,115,2403,2,2,1,12,1,Meṇḍakapañho 
532506,115,2404,2,17,1,147,15,Aparasmiṃ divase rājā katapātarāso pāsādassa dīghantare caṅkamanto vātapānantarena olokento ekaṃ eḷakañca sunakhañca mittasanthavaṃ karontaṃ addasa. 
532507,115,2404,18,28,1,78,10,So kira eḷako hatthisālaṃ gantvā hatthissa purato khittaṃ anāmaṭṭhatiṇaṃ khādi. 
532508,115,2404,29,34,1,40,5,Atha naṃ hatthigopakā pothetvā nīhariṃsu. 
532509,115,2404,35,38,1,19,3,So viravitvā palāyi. 
532510,115,2404,39,48,1,65,9,Atha naṃ eko puriso vegenāgantvā piṭṭhiyaṃ daṇḍena tiriyaṃ pahari. 
532511,115,2404,49,60,1,96,11,So piṭṭhiṃ onāmetvā vedanāppatto hutvā gantvā rājagehassa mahābhittiṃ nissāya piṭṭhikāya nipajji. 
532512,115,2404,61,89,1,251,26,Taṃ divasameva rañño mahānase aṭṭhicammādīni khāditvā vaḍḍhitasunakho bhattakārake bhattaṃ sampādetvā bahi ṭhatvā sarīre sedaṃ nibbāpente macchamaṃsagandhaṃ ghāyitvā taṇhaṃ adhivāsetuṃ asakkonto mahānasaṃ pavisitvā bhājanapidhānaṃ pātetvā maṃsaṃ khādi. 
532513,115,2404,90,101,1,96,11,Atha bhattakārako bhājanasaddena pavisitvā taṃ disvā dvāraṃ pidahitvā taṃ leḍḍudaṇḍādīhi pothesi. 
532514,115,2404,102,108,1,55,6,So khāditamaṃsaṃ mukheneva chaḍḍetvā viravitvā nikkhami. 
532515,115,2404,109,118,1,88,9,Bhattakārakopi tassa nikkhantabhāvaṃ ñatvā anubandhitvā piṭṭhiyaṃ daṇḍena tiriyaṃ pahari. 
532516,115,2404,119,129,1,88,10,So vedanāppatto piṭṭhiṃ onāmetvā ekaṃ pādaṃ ukkhipitvā eḷakassa nipannaṭṭhānameva pāvisi. 
532517,115,2404,130,150,1,82,14,"Atha naṃ eḷako‘‘ samma, kiṃ piṭṭhiṃ onāmetvā āgacchasi, kiṃ te vāto vijjhatī’’ ti pucchi. "
532518,115,2404,151,167,1,74,11,"Sunakhopi‘‘ tvampi piṭṭhiṃ onāmetvā nipannosi, kiṃ te vāto vijjhatī’’ ti pucchi. "
532519,115,2404,168,173,1,38,5,Te aññamaññaṃ attano pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. 
532520,115,2405,2,19,1,80,13,Atha naṃ eḷako pucchi‘‘ kiṃ pana tvaṃ puna bhattagehaṃ gantuṃ sakkhissasi sammā’’ ti?
532521,115,2405,20,34,1,49,8,"‘‘ Na sakkhissāmi, samma, gatassa me jīvitaṃ natthī’’ ti."
532522,115,2405,35,46,1,48,7,‘‘ Tvaṃ pana puna hatthisālaṃ gantuṃ sakkhissasī’’ ti.
532523,115,2405,47,62,1,58,10,"‘‘ Mayāpi tattha gantuṃ na sakkā, gatassa me jīvitaṃ natthī’’ ti. "
532524,115,2405,63,77,1,57,10,Te‘‘ kathaṃ nu kho mayaṃ idāni jīvissāmā’’ ti upāyaṃ cintesuṃ. 
532525,115,2405,78,82,1,18,4,Atha naṃ eḷako āha–
532526,115,2405,83,97,1,56,8,"‘‘ sace mayaṃ samaggavāsaṃ vasituṃ sakkoma, attheko upāyo’’ ti."
532527,115,2405,98,106,1,18,4,‘‘ Tena hi kathehī’’ ti.
532528,115,2405,107,135,1,130,19,"‘‘ Samma, tvaṃ ito paṭṭhāya hatthisālaṃ yāhi,‘‘ nāyaṃ tiṇaṃ khādatī’’ ti tayi hatthigopakā āsaṅkaṃ na karissanti, tvaṃ mama tiṇaṃ āhareyyāsi. "
532529,115,2405,136,160,1,120,16,"Ahampi bhattagehaṃ pavisissāmi,‘‘ nāyaṃ maṃsakhādako’’ ti bhattakārako mayi āsaṅkaṃ na karissati, ahaṃ te maṃsaṃ āharissāmī’’ ti. "
532530,115,2405,161,171,1,41,6,Te‘‘ sundaro upāyo’’ ti ubhopi sampaṭicchiṃsu. 
532531,115,2405,172,180,1,84,8,Sunakho hatthisālaṃ gantvā tiṇakalāpaṃ ḍaṃsitvā āgantvā mahābhittipiṭṭhikāya ṭhapesi. 
532532,115,2405,181,190,1,83,9,Itaropi bhattagehaṃ gantvā maṃsakhaṇḍaṃ mukhapūraṃ ḍaṃsitvā ānetvā tattheva ṭhapesi. 
532533,115,2405,191,198,1,38,6,"Sunakho maṃsaṃ khādi, eḷako tiṇaṃ khādi. "
532534,115,2405,199,206,1,65,7,Te iminā upāyena samaggā sammodamānā mahābhittipiṭṭhikāya vasanti. 
532535,115,2405,207,225,1,121,15,"Rājā tesaṃ mittasanthavaṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ adiṭṭhapubbaṃ vata me kāraṇaṃ diṭṭhaṃ, ime paccāmittā hutvāpi samaggavāsaṃ vasanti. "
532536,115,2405,226,252,1,165,21,"Idaṃ kāraṇaṃ gahetvā pañhaṃ katvā pañca paṇḍite pucchissāmi, imaṃ pañhaṃ ajānantaṃ raṭṭhā pabbājessāmi, taṃ jānantassa‘ evarūpo paṇḍito natthī’ ti mahāsakkāraṃ karissāmi. "
532537,115,2405,253,264,1,55,8,"Ajja tāva avelā, sve upaṭṭhānaṃ āgatakāle pucchissāmī’’ ti. "
532538,115,2405,265,274,1,73,9,So punadivase paṇḍitesu āgantvā nisinnesu pañhaṃ pucchanto imaṃ gāthamāha–
532539,115,2406,2,13,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Yesaṃ na kadāci bhūtapubbaṃ, sakhyaṃ sattapadampimasmi loke; "
532540,115,2407,2,24,1,58,9,"Jātā amittā duve sahāyā, paṭisandhāya caranti kissa hetū’’ ti.( jā.1.12.94); "
532541,115,2408,2,8,1,46,5,Tattha {paṭisandhāyā}ti saddahitvā ghaṭitā hutvā. 
532542,115,2409,2,7,1,30,5,Idañca pana vatvā puna evamāha–
532543,115,2410,2,13,1,60,9,"‘ ‘ Yadi me ajja pātarāsakāle, pañhaṃ na sakkuṇeyyātha vattumetaṃ; "
532544,115,2411,2,24,1,63,9,"Raṭṭhā pabbājayissāmi vo sabbe, na hi mattho duppaññajātikehī’’ ti.( jā.1.12.95); "
532545,115,2412,2,13,1,70,10,"Tadā pana senako aggāsane nisinno ahosi, paṇḍito pana pariyante nisinno. "
532546,115,2412,14,53,1,259,31,"So taṃ pañhaṃ upadhārento tamatthaṃ adisvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ rājā dandhadhātuko imaṃ pañhaṃ cintetvā saṅkharituṃ asamattho, kiñcideva, tena diṭṭhaṃ bhavissati, ekadivasaṃ okāsaṃ labhanto imaṃ pañhaṃ nīharissāmi, senako kenaci upāyena ajjekadivasamattaṃ adhivāsāpetū’’ ti. "
532547,115,2412,54,64,1,72,9,Itarepi cattāro paṇḍitā andhakāragabbhaṃ paviṭṭhā viya na kiñci passiṃsu. 
532548,115,2412,65,78,1,60,9,Senako‘‘ kā nu kho mahosadhassa pavattī’’ ti bodhisattaṃ olokesi. 
532549,115,2412,79,82,1,16,3,Sopi taṃ olokesi. 
532550,115,2412,83,144,1,371,46,"Senako bodhisattassa olokitākāreneva tassa adhippāyaṃ ñatvā‘‘ paṇḍitassapi na upaṭṭhāti, tenekadivasaṃ okāsaṃ icchati, pūressāmissa manorathan’’ ti cintetvā raññā saddhiṃ vissāsena mahāhasitaṃ hasitvā‘‘ kiṃ, mahārāja, sabbeva amhe pañhaṃ kathetuṃ asakkonte raṭṭhā pabbājessasi, etampi‘ eko gaṇṭhipañho’ ti tvaṃ sallakkhesi, na mayaṃ etaṃ kathetuṃ na sakkoma, apica kho thokaṃ adhivāsehi. "
532551,115,2412,145,170,1,153,19,"Gaṇṭhipañho esa, na sakkoma mahājanamajjhe kathetuṃ, ekamante cintetvā pacchā tumhākaṃ kathessāma , okāsaṃ no dehī’’ ti mahāsattaṃ oloketvā imaṃ gāthādvayamāha–"
532552,115,2413,2,10,1,53,5,"‘ ‘ Mahājanasamāgamamhi ghore, janakolāhalasaṅgamamhi jāte; "
532553,115,2414,2,9,1,55,6,"Vikkhittamanā anekacittā, pañhaṃ na sakkuṇoma vattumetaṃ."
532554,115,2415,2,11,1,53,7,"‘ ‘ Ekaggacittāva ekamekā, rahasi gatā atthaṃ nicintayitvā; "
532555,115,2416,2,23,1,64,8,"Paviveke sammasitvāna dhīrā, atha vakkhanti janinda etamatthan’’ ti.( jā.1.12.96-97); "
532556,115,2417,2,17,1,106,14,Tattha {sammasitvānā}ti kāyacittaviveke ṭhitā ime dhīrā imaṃ pañhaṃ sammasitvā atha vo etaṃ atthaṃ vakkhanti. 
532557,115,2418,2,22,1,112,15,"Rājā tassa kathaṃ sutvā anattamano hutvāpi‘‘ sādhu cintetvā kathetha, akathente pana vo pabbājessāmī’’ ti tajjesiyeva. "
532558,115,2418,23,27,1,31,4,Cattāro paṇḍitā pāsādā otariṃsu. 
532559,115,2418,28,31,1,16,3,Senako itare āha–
532560,115,2418,32,52,1,114,13,"‘‘ sammā, rājā sukhumapañhaṃ pucchi, akathite mahantaṃ bhayaṃ bhavissati, sappāyabhojanaṃ bhuñjitvā sammā upadhārethā’’ ti. "
532561,115,2418,53,58,1,27,5,Te attano attano gehaṃ gatā. 
532562,115,2418,59,80,1,106,16,"Paṇḍitopi uṭṭhāya udumbaradeviyā santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ devi, ajja vā hiyyo vā rājā kattha ciraṃ aṭṭhāsī’’ ti pucchi."
532563,115,2418,81,92,1,48,6,"‘‘ Tāta, dīghantare vātapānena olokento caṅkamatī’’ ti. "
532564,115,2418,93,107,1,68,10,Tato paṇḍito cintesi‘‘ raññā iminā passena kiñci diṭṭhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. 
532565,115,2418,108,130,1,128,18,So tattha gantvā bahi olokento eḷakasunakhānaṃ kiriyaṃ disvā‘‘ ime disvā raññā pañho abhisaṅkhato’’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ katvā gehaṃ gato. 
