533587,115,2779,45,91,1,259,34,"Tameko paṇḍitassa upanikkhittakapuriso uṭṭhāya gaṇhi, atha taṃ rañño santikaṃ āharitvā‘‘ passatha, deva, imassa daṇḍakaṃ, na no ito pubbe evaṃ dīghadaṇḍako diṭṭhapubbo’’ ti vatvā‘‘ minatha nan’’ ti vutte paṇḍitassa purisā saṭṭhihatthaṃ daṇḍakaṃ asītihatthaṃ katvā miniṃsu. "
533588,115,2779,92,106,1,63,10,Puna raññā‘‘ katthetaṃ jātan’’ ti vutte eko musāvādaṃ katvā evamāha–
533589,115,2779,107,135,1,181,21,"‘‘ deva, ahaṃ ekadivasaṃ pipāsito hutvā‘ suraṃ pivissāmī’ ti cūḷadvārena nagaraṃ paviṭṭho, nāgarānaṃ udakakīḷatthāya kataṃ mahāpokkharaṇiṃ passiṃ, mahājano nāvāya nisīditvā pupphāni gaṇhāti. "
533590,115,2779,136,150,1,90,11,"Tattha idaṃ tīrappadese jātaṃ, gambhīraṭṭhāne jātassa pana daṇḍako satahattho bhavissatī’’ ti. "
