533614,115,2781,245,259,1,84,11,"‘‘ Mahārāja na senā yujjhissanti, dvinnaṃ pana rājūnaṃ dve paṇḍitā ekaṭṭhāne bhavissanti. "
533615,115,2781,260,267,1,44,6,"Tesu yo vandissati, tassa parājayo bhavissati. "
