533676,115,2787,318,346,1,217,24,"Idāni vedehassa ca gahapatiputtassa ca jīvitaṃ natthi, ahaṃ imasmiṃ nagare pākārassa thiraṭṭhānadubbalaṭṭhānañca parikhāyaṃ kumbhīlādīnaṃ atthiṭṭhānañca natthiṭṭhānañca jānāmi, na cirasseva vo nagaraṃ gahetvā dassāmī’’ ti. "
533677,115,2787,347,358,1,81,9,"Atha so rājā saddahitvā tumhākaṃ sakkāraṃ karissati, senāvāhanañca paṭicchāpessati. "
533678,115,2787,359,363,1,50,4,Athassa senaṃ vāḷakumbhīlaṭṭhānesuyeva otāreyyātha. 
533679,115,2787,364,397,1,203,27,"Tassa senā kumbhīlabhayena na otarissati, tadā tumhe rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ tumhākaṃ senāya, deva, gahapatiputtena lañjo dinno, sabbe rājāno ca ācariyakevaṭṭañca ādiṃ katvā na kenaci lañjo aggahito nāma atthi. "
533680,115,2787,398,412,1,101,12,"Kevalaṃ ete tumhe parivāretvā caranti, sabbe pana gahapatiputtassa santakāva, ahamekova tumhākaṃ puriso. "
