533779,115,2802,25,43,1,142,16,"{Āgacchantū}ti ito paṭṭhāya kira uttarapañcālanagarato paṇṇākāraṃ gahetvā madhuravacanā piyabhāṇino dūtā idha āgacchantu, ito ca tattha gacchantu. "
