533794,115,2804,152,169,1,110,15,"Iti so tassa santikaṃ gantvā neva nisīdituṃ, na āsanaṃ nissāya ṭhitaṭṭhānaṃ labhi, allagomayaṃ akkamitvā aṭṭhāsi. "
533795,115,2805,2,17,1,78,12,"Atha naṃ oloketvā eko akkhīni nimīli, eko bhamukaṃ ukkhipi, eko kapparaṃ kaṇḍūyi. "
533796,115,2805,18,57,1,202,27,"So tesaṃ kiriyaṃ oloketvā maṅkubhūto‘‘ gacchāmahaṃ paṇḍitā’’ ti vatvā aparena‘‘ are duṭṭhabrāhmaṇa,‘ mā saddamakāsī’ ti vutto saddameva karosi, aṭṭhīni te bhindissāmī’’ ti vutte bhītatasito hutvā nivattitvā olokesi. "
533797,115,2805,58,74,1,105,14,"Atha naṃ añño veḷupesikāya piṭṭhiyaṃ tālesi, añño gīvāyaṃ gahetvā khipi, añño piṭṭhiyaṃ hatthatalena pahari. "
