536407,116,280,64,83,1,143,16,"Suvavatthitaṃ vavatthapetīti yathā suṭṭhu vavatthitaṃ hoti, na puna antaradhānaṃ gacchati, tathā taṃ satiyā vavatthapeti, upadhāreti upanibandhati. "
