536414,116,282,46,47,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
536415,116,282,48,68,1,164,18,"Uppaṭipāṭiyā hi manasikaronto seyyathāpi nāma akusalo puriso dvattiṃsapadaṃ nisseṇiṃ uppaṭipāṭiyā ārohanto kilantakāyo tato nisseṇito papatati, na ārohanaṃ sampādeti; "
536416,116,282,69,81,1,139,11,"evameva bhāvanāsampattivasena adhigantabbassa assādassa anadhigamanato kilantacitto dvattiṃsākārabhāvanāto papatati, na bhāvanaṃ sampādetīti. "
536417,116,283,2,11,1,70,9,Anupubbato manasikarontopi ca kesā lomāti nātisīghato pi manasi karoti. 
536418,116,283,12,34,1,203,20,"Atisīghato hi manasikaronto seyyathāpi nāma addhānaṃ gacchanto puriso samavisamarukkhathalaninnadvedhāpathādīni magganimittāni upalakkhetuṃ na sakkoti, tato na maggakusalo hoti, addhānañca parikkhayaṃ neti; "
536419,116,283,35,52,1,138,14,"evameva vaṇṇasaṇṭhānādīni dvattiṃsākāranimittāni upalakkhetuṃ na sakkoti, tato na dvattiṃsākāre kusalo hoti, kammaṭṭhānañca parikkhayaṃ neti. "
536420,116,284,2,11,1,55,8,"Yathā ca nātisīghato, evaṃ nātisaṇikato pi manasi karoti. "
536421,116,284,12,29,1,205,17,Atisaṇikato hi manasikaronto seyyathāpi nāma puriso addhānamaggaṃ paṭipanno antarāmagge rukkhapabbatataḷākādīsu vilambamāno icchitappadesaṃ apāpuṇanto antarāmaggeyeva sīhabyagghādīhi anayabyasanaṃ pāpuṇāti; 
536422,116,284,30,39,1,115,8,evameva dvattiṃsākārabhāvanāsampadaṃ apāpuṇanto bhāvanāvicchedena antarāyeva kāmavitakkādīhi anayabyasanaṃ pāpuṇāti. 
536423,116,285,2,9,1,66,7,Nātisaṇikato manasikarontopi ca vikkhepappahānato pi manasi karoti. 
536424,116,285,10,22,1,90,11,"Vikkhepappahānato nāma yathā aññesu navakammādīsu cittaṃ na vikkhipati, tathā manasi karoti. "
536425,116,285,23,37,1,165,14,Bahiddhā vikkhepamānacitto hi kesādīsveva asamāhitacetovitakko bhāvanāsampadaṃ apāpuṇitvā antarāva anayabyasanaṃ āpajjati takkasilāgamane bodhisattassa sahāyakā viya. 
536426,116,285,38,47,1,121,9,Avikkhipamānacitto pana kesādīsveva samāhitacetovitakko bhāvanāsampadaṃ pāpuṇāti bodhisatto viya takkasilarajjasampadanti. 
536427,116,285,48,62,1,129,14,Tassevaṃ vikkhepappahānato manasikaroto adhikāracariyādhimuttīnaṃ vasena te dhammā asubhato vā vaṇṇato vā suññato vā upaṭṭhahanti. 
536428,116,286,2,8,1,52,6,Atha paṇṇattisamatikkamanato te dhamme manasi karoti. 
536429,116,286,9,21,1,133,11,{Paṇṇattisamatikkamanato}ti kesā lomāti evamādivohāraṃ samatikkamitvā vissajjetvā yathūpaṭṭhitānaṃ asubhādīnaṃyeva vasena manasi karoti. 
536430,116,286,22,24,1,6,1,Kathaṃ ? 
536431,116,286,25,74,1,481,45,"Yathā araññanivāsūpagatā manussā aparicitabhūmibhāgattā udakaṭṭhānasañjānanatthaṃ sākhābhaṅgādinimittaṃ katvā tadanusārena gantvā udakaṃ paribhuñjanti, yadā pana paricitabhūmibhāgā honti, atha taṃ nimittaṃ vissajjetvā amanasikatvāva udakaṭṭhānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā udakaṃ paribhuñjanti, evamevāyaṃ kesā lomātiādinā taṃtaṃvohārassa vasena paṭhamaṃ te dhamme manasākāsi, tesu dhammesu asubhādīnaṃ aññataravasena upaṭṭhahantesu taṃ vohāraṃ samatikkamitvā vissajjetvā asubhāditova manasi karoti. "
536432,116,287,2,33,1,164,22,"Etthāha ‘‘ kathaṃ panassa ete dhammā asubhādito upaṭṭhahanti, kathaṃ vaṇṇato, kathaṃ suññato vā, kathañcāyamete asubhato manasi karoti, kathaṃ vaṇṇato, kathaṃ suññato vā’’ ti? "
536433,116,287,34,47,1,121,12,"Kesā tāvassa vaṇṇasaṇṭhānagandhāsayokāsavasena pañcadhā asubhato upaṭṭhahanti, pañcadhā eva ayamete asubhato manasi karoti. "
536434,116,287,48,57,1,62,6,Seyyathidaṃ– kesā nāmete vaṇṇato asubhā paramappaṭikūlajegucchā . 
536435,116,287,58,77,1,142,19,Tathā hi manussā divā pānabhojane patitaṃ kesavaṇṇaṃ vākaṃ vā suttaṃ vā disvā kesasaññāya manoramampi pānabhojanaṃ chaḍḍenti vā jigucchanti vā. 
536436,116,287,78,80,1,19,2,Saṇṭhānatopi asubhā. 
536437,116,287,81,99,1,142,18,Tathā hi rattiṃ pānabhojane patitaṃ kesasaṇṭhānaṃ vākaṃ vā suttaṃ vā phusitvā kesasaññāya manoramampi pānabhojanaṃ chaḍḍenti vā jigucchanti vā. 
536438,116,287,100,102,1,17,2,Gandhatopi asubhā. 
536439,116,287,103,123,1,179,18,"Tathā hi telamakkhanapupphadhūmādisaṅkhārehi virahitānaṃ kesānaṃ gandho paramajeguccho hoti, aggīsu pakkhittassa kesassa gandhaṃ ghāyitvā sattā nāsikaṃ pidhenti, mukhampi vikujjenti. "
536440,116,287,124,126,1,16,2,Āsayatopi asubhā. 
536441,116,287,127,141,1,154,14,Tathā hi nānāvidhena manussāsucinissandena saṅkāraṭṭhāne taṇḍuleyyakādīni viya pittasemhapubbalohitanissandena te ācitā vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ gamitāti. 
536442,116,287,142,144,1,16,2,Okāsatopi asubhā. 
536443,116,287,145,156,1,136,11,Tathā hi saṅkāraṭṭhāne viya taṇḍuleyyakādīni paramajegucche lomādiekatiṃsakuṇaparāsimatthake manussānaṃ sīsapaliveṭhake allacamme jātāti. 
