536447,116,288,12,16,1,36,4,Tathā lomā dantā odātakasiṇavasenāti. 
536448,116,288,17,21,1,18,3,Esa nayo sabbattha . 
536449,116,288,22,33,1,90,10,"Taṃtaṃkasiṇavaseneva ayamete manasi karoti, evaṃ vaṇṇato upaṭṭhahante vaṇṇato manasi karoti. "
