536526,116,324,2,33,1,234,27,"Idāni tesaṃ atthavaṇṇanā hoti– ekaṃ nāma kin ti bhagavā yasmiṃ ekadhammasmiṃ bhikkhu sammā nibbindamāno anupubbena dukkhassantakaro hoti, yasmiṃ cāyamāyasmā nibbindamāno anupubbena dukkhassantamakāsi, taṃ dhammaṃ sandhāya pañhaṃ pucchati."
536527,116,324,34,46,1,73,8,‘‘ Sabbe sattā āhāraṭṭhitikā’’ ti thero puggalādhiṭṭhānāya desanāya vissajjeti.
536528,116,324,47,55,1,29,4,"‘‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sammāsati? "
