537097,116,527,2,21,1,102,10,"Ettha ca‘‘ jetavane’’ ti vacanaṃ purimasāmiparikittanaṃ,‘‘ anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme’’ ti pacchimasāmiparikittanaṃ. "
