537381,116,613,2,58,1,346,43,"4. Evaṃ bhagavā‘‘ brūhi maṅgalamuttaman’’ ti ekaṃ ajjhesitopi appaṃ yācito bahudāyako uḷārapuriso viya ekāya gāthāya tīṇi maṅgalāni vatvā tato uttaripi devatānaṃ sotukāmatāya maṅgalānamatthitāya yesaṃ yesaṃ yaṃ yaṃ anukulaṃ, te te satte tattha tattha maṅgale niyojetukāmatāya ca‘‘ patirūpadesavāso cā’’ tiādīhi gāthāhi punapi anekāni maṅgalāni vattumāraddho. "
