537390,116,614,2,30,1,223,24,"Atthavaṇṇanā pana evaṃ veditabbā– patirūpadesavāso nāma yattha catasso parisā vicaranti, dānādīni puññakiriyavatthūni vattanti, navaṅgaṃ satthu sāsanaṃ dibbati, tattha nivāso sattānaṃ puññakiriyāya paccayattā maṅgalanti vuccati. "
