538301,116,898,2,3,1,26,2,Varo varaññūtigāthāvaṇṇanā 
538302,116,899,2,21,1,114,12,14. Evaṃ bhagavā pariyattidhammena buddhādhiṭṭhānaṃ saccaṃ vatvā idāni lokuttaradhammena vattumāraddho‘‘ varo varaññū’’ ti. 
538303,116,899,22,44,1,120,16,"Tattha {varo}ti paṇītādhimuttikehi icchito‘‘ aho vata mayampi evarūpā assāmā’’ ti, varaguṇayogato vā varo uttamo seṭṭhoti attho. "
538304,116,899,45,49,1,20,2,{Varaññū}ti nibbānaññū. 
538305,116,899,50,60,1,89,9,"Nibbānañhi sabbadhammānaṃ uttamaṭṭhena varaṃ, tañcesa bodhimūle sayaṃ paṭivijjhitvā aññāsi. "
538306,116,899,61,68,1,121,6,{Varado}ti pañcavaggiyabhaddavaggiyajaṭilādīnaṃ aññesañca devamanussānaṃ nibbedhabhāgiyavāsanābhāgiyavaradhammadāyīti attho. 
538307,116,899,69,76,1,55,6,{Varāharo}ti varassa maggassa āhaṭattā varāharoti vuccati. 
538308,116,899,77,98,1,143,16,"So hi bhagavā dīpaṅkarato pabhuti samatiṃsa pāramiyo pūrento pubbakehi sammāsambuddhehi anuyātaṃ purāṇamaggavaramāhari, tena‘‘ varāharo’’ ti vuccati. "
538309,116,900,2,15,1,135,10,"Apica sabbaññutaññāṇappaṭilābhena varo, nibbānasacchikiriyāya varaññū, sattānaṃ vimuttisukhadānena varado, uttamapaṭipadāharaṇena varāharo. "
538310,116,900,16,23,1,65,7,Etehi lokuttaraguṇehi adhikassa kassaci guṇassa abhāvato anuttaro. 
538311,116,901,2,19,1,173,12,"Aparo nayo– varo upasamādhiṭṭhānaparipūraṇena, varaññū paññādhiṭṭhānaparipūraṇena, varado cāgādhiṭṭhānaparipūraṇena, varāharo saccādhiṭṭhānaparipūraṇena, varaṃ maggasaccamāharīti. "
538312,116,901,20,54,1,333,28,"Tathā varo puññussayena, varaññū paññussayena, varado buddhabhāvatthikānaṃ tadupāyasampadānena, varāharo paccekabuddhabhāvatthikānaṃ tadupāyāharaṇena, anuttaro tattha tattha asadisatāya, attanā vā anācariyako hutvā paresaṃ ācariyabhāvena, dhammavaraṃ adesayi sāvakabhāvatthikānaṃ tadatthāya svākkhātatādiguṇayuttassa dhammavarassa desanato. "
538313,116,901,55,57,1,21,2,Sesaṃ vuttanayamevāti. 
538314,116,902,2,24,1,145,17,Evaṃ bhagavā navavidhena lokuttaradhammena attano guṇaṃ vatvā idāni tameva guṇaṃ nissāya buddhādhiṭṭhānaṃ saccavacanaṃ payuñjati‘‘ idampi buddhe’’ ti. 
538315,116,902,25,29,1,39,4,Tassattho pubbe vuttanayeneva veditabbo. 
538316,116,902,30,53,1,135,19,"Kevalaṃ pana yaṃ varaṃ lokuttaradhammaṃ esa aññāsi, yañca adāsi, yañca āhari, yañca desesi, idampi buddhe ratanaṃ paṇītanti evaṃ yojetabbaṃ. "
