538343,116,908,2,2,1,26,1,Yānīdhātigāthāttayavaṇṇanā 
538344,116,909,2,88,1,490,62,"16. Atha sakko devānamindo‘‘ bhagavatā ratanattayaguṇaṃ nissāya saccavacanaṃ payuñjamānena nāgarassa sotthi katā, mayāpi nāgarassa sotthitthaṃ ratanattayaguṇaṃ nissāya kiñci vattabban’’ ti cintetvā avasāne gāthāttayaṃ abhāsi‘‘ yānīdha bhūtānī’’ ti tattha yasmā buddho yathā lokahitatthāya ussukkaṃ āpannehi āgantabbaṃ , tathā āgatato yathā ca tehi gantabbaṃ, tathā gatato yathā ca tehi ājānitabbaṃ, tathā ājānanato, yathā ca jānitabbaṃ, tathā jānanato, yañca tatheva hoti, tassa gadanato ca‘‘ tathāgato’’ ti vuccati. "
538345,116,909,89,126,1,273,30,"Yasmā ca so devamanussehi pupphagandhādinā bahi nibbattena upakārakena, dhammānudhammapaṭipattādinā ca attani nibbattena ativiya pūjito, tasmā sakko devānamindo sabbaṃ devaparisaṃ attanā saddhiṃ sampiṇḍetvā āha‘‘ tathāgataṃ devamanussapūjitaṃ, buddhaṃ namassāma suvatthi hotū’’ ti. "
538346,116,910,2,18,1,132,12,"17. Yasmā pana dhamme maggadhammo yathā yuganaddhasamathavipassanābalena gantabbaṃ kilesapakkhaṃ samucchindantena, tathā gatoti tathāgato. "
538347,116,910,19,39,1,137,14,"Nibbānadhammopi yathā gato paññāya paṭividdho sabbadukkhappaṭivighātāya sampajjati, buddhādīhi tathā avagato, tasmā‘‘ tathāgato’’ tveva vuccati. "
538348,116,910,40,60,1,111,15,"Yasmā ca saṅghopi yathā attahitāya paṭipannehi gantabbaṃ tena tena maggena, tathā gatoti‘‘ tathāgato’’ tveva vuccati. "
538349,116,910,61,76,1,120,13,"Tasmā avasesagāthādvayepi tathāgataṃ dhammaṃ namassāma suvatthi hotu, tathāgataṃ saṅghaṃ namassāma suvatthi {hotū}ti vuttaṃ. "
538350,116,910,77,79,1,21,2,Sesaṃ vuttanayamevāti. 
538351,116,911,2,16,1,117,13,Evaṃ sakko devānamindo imaṃ gāthāttayaṃ bhāsitvā bhagavantaṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā devapurameva gato saddhiṃ devaparisāya. 
538352,116,911,17,40,1,185,20,"Bhagavā pana tadeva ratanasuttaṃ dutiyadivasepi desesi, puna caturāsītiyā pāṇasahassānaṃ dhammābhisamayo ahosi, evaṃ yāva sattamadivasaṃ desesi, divase divase tatheva dhammābhisamayo ahosi. "
538353,116,911,41,53,1,72,8,Bhagavā aḍḍhamāsameva vesāliyaṃ viharitvā rājūnaṃ‘‘ gacchāmā’’ ti paṭivedesi. 
538354,116,911,54,66,1,80,10,Tato rājāno diguṇena sakkārena puna tīhi divasehi bhagavantaṃ gaṅgātīraṃ nayiṃsu. 
538355,116,911,67,105,1,274,29,"Gaṅgāya nibbattā nāgarājāno cintesuṃ‘‘ manussā tathāgatassa sakkāraṃ karonti, mayaṃ kiṃ na karissāmā’’ ti suvaṇṇarajatamaṇimayā nāvāyo māpetvā suvaṇṇarajatamaṇimaye eva pallaṅke paññapetvā pañcavaṇṇapadumasañchannaṃ udakaṃ karitvā‘‘ amhākaṃ anuggahaṃ karothā’’ ti bhagavantaṃ yāciṃsu. "
538356,116,911,106,116,1,88,9,"Bhagavā adhivāsetvā ratananāvamārūḷho, pañca ca bhikkhusatāni pañcasataṃ nāvāyo abhirūḷhā. "
538357,116,911,117,123,1,69,6,Nāgarājāno bhagavantaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena nāgabhavanaṃ pavesesuṃ. 
538358,116,911,124,131,1,59,7,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā sabbarattiṃ nāgaparisāya dhammaṃ desesi. 
538359,116,911,132,142,1,98,9,"Dutiyadivase dibbehi khādanīyabhojanīyehi mahādānaṃ akaṃsu, bhagavā anumoditvā nāgabhavanā nikkhami. "
538360,116,912,2,25,1,156,18,"Bhūmaṭṭhā devā‘‘ manussā ca nāgā ca tathāgatassa sakkāraṃ karonti, mayaṃ kiṃ na karissāmā’’ ti cintetvā vanappagumbarukkhapabbatādīsu chattātichattāni ukkhipiṃsu. "
538361,116,912,26,34,1,76,7,"Eteneva upāyena yāva akaniṭṭhabrahmabhavanaṃ, tāva mahāsakkāraviseso nibbatti. "
538362,116,912,35,40,1,59,5,Bimbisāropi licchavīhi āgatakāle katasakkārato diguṇamakāsi. 
538363,116,912,41,48,1,64,7,Pubbe vuttanayeneva pañcahi divasehi bhagavantaṃ rājagahaṃ ānesi. 
538364,116,913,2,51,1,385,41,"Rājagahamanuppatte bhagavati pacchābhattaṃ maṇḍalamāḷe sannipatitānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ ayamantarakathā udapādi‘‘ aho buddhassa bhagavato ānubhāvo, yaṃ uddissa gaṅgāya orato ca pārato ca aṭṭhayojano bhūmibhāgo ninnañca thalañca samaṃ katvā vālukāya okiritvā pupphehi sañchanno, yojanappamāṇaṃ gaṅgāya udakaṃ nānāvaṇṇehi padumehi sañchannaṃ, yāva akaniṭṭhabhavanaṃ, tāva chattātichattāni ussitānī’’ ti. "
538365,116,913,52,65,1,130,12,Bhagavā taṃ pavattiṃ ñatvā gandhakuṭito nikkhamitvā taṅkhaṇānurūpena pāṭihāriyena gantvā maṇḍalamāḷe paññattavarabuddhāsane nisīdi. 
538366,116,913,66,71,1,36,5,Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
538367,116,913,72,85,1,51,7,"‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti. "
538368,116,913,86,92,1,41,5,Bhikkhū sabbaṃ ārocesuṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
538369,116,913,93,116,1,145,15,"‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ayaṃ pūjāviseso mayhaṃ buddhānubhāvena nibbatto, na nāgadevabrahmānubhāvena, apica kho pubbe appamattakapariccāgānubhāvena nibbatto’’ ti. "
538370,116,913,117,144,1,125,19,"Bhikkhū āhaṃsu‘‘ na mayaṃ, bhante, taṃ appamattakaṃ pariccāgaṃ jānāma, sādhu no bhagavā tathā kathetu, yathā mayaṃ taṃ jāneyyāmā’’ ti. "
538371,116,914,2,14,1,73,9,"Bhagavā āha– bhūtapubbaṃ, bhikkhave, takkasilāyaṃ saṅkho nāma brāhmaṇo ahosi. "
538372,116,914,15,22,1,56,7,Tassa putto susīmo nāma māṇavo soḷasavassuddesiko vayena. 
538373,116,914,23,30,1,65,7,So ekadivasaṃ pitaraṃ upasaṅkamitvā abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
538374,116,914,31,45,1,36,8,"Atha taṃ pitā āha‘‘ kiṃ, tāta, susīmā’’ ti? "
538375,116,914,46,61,1,59,9,"So āha‘‘ icchāmahaṃ, tāta, bārāṇasiṃ gantvā sippaṃ uggahetun’’ ti."
538376,116,914,62,87,1,111,16,"‘‘ Tena hi , tāta, susīma, asuko nāma brāhmaṇo mama sahāyako, tassa santikaṃ gantvā uggaṇhāhī’’ ti kahāpaṇasahassaṃ adāsi. "
538377,116,914,88,103,1,140,15,So taṃ gahetvā mātāpitaro abhivādetvā anupubbena bārāṇasiṃ gantvā upacārayuttena vidhinā ācariyaṃ upasaṅkamitvā abhivādetvā attānaṃ nivedesi. 
538378,116,914,104,117,1,84,9,Ācariyo‘‘ mama sahāyakassa putto’’ ti māṇavaṃ sampaṭicchitvā sabbaṃ pāhuneyyavattamakāsi. 
538379,116,914,118,130,1,109,12,So addhānakilamathaṃ vinodetvā taṃ kahāpaṇasahassaṃ ācariyassa pādamūle ṭhapetvā sippaṃ uggahetuṃ okāsaṃ yāci. 
538380,116,914,131,135,1,32,4,Ācariyo okāsaṃ katvā uggaṇhāpesi. 
538381,116,915,2,19,1,161,14,"So lahuñca gaṇhanto, bahuñca gaṇhanto, gahitagahitañca suvaṇṇabhājane pakkhittatelamiva avinassamānaṃ dhārento, dvādasavassikaṃ sippaṃ katipayamāseneva pariyosāpesi. "
538382,116,915,20,28,1,58,7,"So sajjhāyaṃ karonto ādimajjhaṃyeva passati, no pariyosānaṃ. "
538383,116,915,29,46,1,87,11,"Atha ācariyaṃ upasaṅkamitvā āha‘‘ imassa sippassa ādimajjhameva passāmi, no pariyosānan’’ ti. "
538384,116,915,47,59,1,34,6,"Ācariyo āha‘‘ ahampi, tāta, evamevā’’ ti. "
538385,116,915,60,69,1,52,7,"Atha ko, ācariya, imassa sippassa pariyosānaṃ jānātīti? "
538386,116,915,70,79,1,40,6,"Isipatane, tāta, isayo atthi, te jāneyyunti. "
538387,116,915,80,85,1,35,4,"Te upasaṅkamitvā pucchāmi, ācariyāti? "
538388,116,915,86,91,1,25,3,"Puccha, tāta, yathāsukhanti. "
538389,116,915,92,109,1,89,11,"So isipatanaṃ gantvā paccekabuddhe upasaṅkamitvā pucchi‘‘ api, bhante, pariyosānaṃ jānāthā’’ ti? "
538390,116,915,110,115,1,18,3,"Āma, āvuso, jānāmāti. "
538391,116,915,116,119,1,23,3,Taṃ mampi sikkhāpethāti. 
538392,116,915,120,129,1,57,7,"Tena hāvuso, pabbajāhi, na sakkā apabbajitena sikkhāpetunti. "
538393,116,915,130,147,1,80,12,"Sādhu, bhante, pabbājetha vā maṃ, yaṃ vā icchatha, taṃ katvā pariyosānaṃ jānāpethāti. "
538394,116,915,148,168,1,132,15,"Te taṃ pabbājetvā kammaṭṭhāne niyojetuṃ asamatthā‘‘ evaṃ te nivāsetabbaṃ, evaṃ pārupitabban’’ tiādinā nayena ābhisamācārikaṃ sikkhāpesuṃ. "
538395,116,915,169,177,1,81,8,So tattha sikkhanto upanissayasampannattā na cireneva paccekabodhiṃ abhisambujjhi. 
538396,116,915,178,189,1,92,7,Sakalabārāṇasiyaṃ‘‘ susīmapaccekabuddho’’ ti pākaṭo ahosi lābhaggayasaggappatto sampannaparivāro. 
538397,116,915,190,197,1,67,7,So appāyukasaṃvattanikassa kammassa katattā na cireneva parinibbāyi. 
538398,116,915,198,210,1,106,12,Tassa paccekabuddhā ca mahājanakāyo ca sarīrakiccaṃ katvā dhātuyo gahetvā nagaradvāre thūpaṃ patiṭṭhāpesuṃ. 
538399,116,916,2,61,1,325,45,"Atha kho saṅkho brāhmaṇo‘‘ putto me ciragato, na cassa pavattiṃ jānāmī’’ ti puttaṃ daṭṭhukāmo takkasilāya nikkhamitvā anupubbena bārāṇasiṃ gantvā mahājanakāyaṃ sannipatitaṃ disvā‘‘ addhā bahūsu ekopi me puttassa pavattiṃ jānissatī’’ ti cintento upasaṅkamitvā pucchi‘‘ susīmo nāma māṇavo idha āgato atthi, api nu tassa pavattiṃ jānāthā’’ ti? "
538400,116,916,62,96,1,220,25,"Te‘‘ āma, brāhmaṇa, jānāma, imasmiṃ nagare brāhmaṇassa santike tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū hutvā paccekabuddhānaṃ santike pabbajitvā paccekabuddho hutvā anupādisesāya nibbānadhātuyā parinibbāyi, ayamassa thūpo patiṭṭhāpito’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
538401,116,916,97,133,1,318,35,So bhūmiṃ hatthena paharitvā roditvā ca paridevitvā ca taṃ cetiyaṅgaṇaṃ gantvā tiṇāni uddharitvā uttarasāṭakena vālukaṃ ānetvā paccekabuddhacetiyaṅgaṇe okiritvā kamaṇḍaluto udakena samantato bhūmiṃ paripphositvā vanapupphehi pūjaṃ katvā uttarasāṭakena paṭākaṃ āropetvā thūpassa upari attano chattaṃ bandhitvā pakkāmīti. 
538402,116,917,2,11,1,86,9,Evaṃ atītaṃ desetvā jātakaṃ paccuppannena anusandhento bhikkhūnaṃ dhammakathaṃ kathesi.
538403,116,917,12,62,1,311,40,"‘‘ Siyā kho pana vo, bhikkhave, evamassa‘ añño nūna tena samayena saṅkho brāhmaṇo ahosī’ ti, na kho panetaṃ evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ, ahaṃ tena samayena saṅkho brāhmaṇo ahosiṃ, mayā susīmassa paccekabuddhassa cetiyaṅgaṇe tiṇāni uddhaṭāni, tassa me kammassa nissandena aṭṭhayojanamaggaṃ vigatakhāṇukaṇṭakaṃ katvā samaṃ suddhamakaṃsu. "
