538502,116,946,2,2,1,19,1,Paṭhamagāthāvaṇṇanā 
538503,116,947,2,12,1,61,6,1. Idāni imassa tirokuṭṭassa yathākkamaṃ atthavaṇṇanaṃ karissāma. 
538504,116,947,13,22,1,71,7,Seyyathidaṃ– paṭhamagāthāya tāva {tirokuṭṭā}ti kuṭṭānaṃ parabhāgā vuccanti. 
538505,116,947,23,27,1,58,3,{Tiṭṭhantī}ti nisajjādippaṭikkhepato ṭhānakappanavacanametaṃ. 
538506,116,947,28,57,1,185,19,"Tena yathā pākāraparabhāgaṃ pabbataparabhāgañca gacchantaṃ‘‘ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamāno gacchatī’’ ti vadanti, evamidhāpi kuṭṭassa parabhāgesu tiṭṭhante‘‘ tirokuṭṭesu tiṭṭhantī’’ ti āha. "
538507,116,947,58,68,1,107,8,Sandhisiṅghāṭakesu {cā}ti ettha {sandhiyo}ti catukkoṇaracchā vuccanti gharasandhibhittisandhiālokasandhiyo cāpi. 
