538683,116,1023,2,18,1,91,10,"Idāni yadidaṃ tirokuṭṭānantaraṃ‘‘ nidhiṃ nidheti puriso’’ tiādinā nidhikaṇḍaṃ nikkhittaṃ, tassa–"
