538686,116,1026,2,8,1,51,6,Tattha idha nikkhepakāraṇaṃ tāvassa evaṃ veditabbaṃ. 
538687,116,1026,9,24,1,135,14,"Idañhi nidhikaṇḍaṃ bhagavatā iminā anukkamena avuttampi yasmā anumodanavasena vuttassa tirokuṭṭassa mithunabhūtaṃ, tasmā idha nikkhittaṃ. "
