538690,116,1027,2,2,1,15,1,Suttaṭṭhuppatti 
538691,116,1028,2,12,1,82,9,Aṭṭhuppatti panassa– sāvatthiyaṃ kira aññataro kuṭumbiko aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo. 
538692,116,1028,13,23,1,72,9,"So ca saddho hoti pasanno, vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati. "
538693,116,1028,24,31,1,63,7,So ekasmiṃ divase buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa dānaṃ deti. 
538694,116,1028,32,56,1,115,17,"Tena ca samayena rājā dhanatthiko hoti, so tassa santike purisaṃ pesesi‘‘ gaccha, bhaṇe, itthannāmaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ ānehī’’ ti. "
538695,116,1028,57,71,1,58,10,So gantvā taṃ kuṭumbikaṃ āha‘‘ rājā taṃ gahapati āmantetī’’ ti. 
538696,116,1028,72,98,1,164,18,"Kuṭumbiko saddhādiguṇasamannāgatena cetasā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ parivisanto āha‘‘ gaccha, bho purisa, pacchā āgamissāmi, idāni tāvamhi nidhiṃ nidhento ṭhito’’ ti. "
538697,116,1028,99,122,1,159,19,Atha bhagavā bhuttāvī pavārito tameva puññasampadaṃ paramatthato nidhīti dassetuṃ tassa kuṭumbikassa anumodanatthaṃ‘‘ nidhiṃ nidheti puriso’’ ti imā gāthāyo abhāsi. 
