538712,116,1034,12,31,1,132,17,"Kāmañca purisopi itthīpi paṇḍakopi nidhiṃ nidheti, idha pana purisasīsena desanā katā, atthato pana tesampi idha samodhānaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
538713,116,1034,32,41,1,83,7,"Gambhīre {odakantike}ti ogāhetabbaṭṭhena gambhīraṃ, udakassa antikabhāvena odakantikaṃ. "
538714,116,1034,42,77,1,252,31,"Atthi gambhīraṃ na odakantikaṃ jaṅgale bhūmibhāge satikaporiso āvāṭo viya, atthi odakantikaṃ na gambhīraṃ ninne pallale ekadvividatthiko āvāṭo viya, atthi gambhīrañceva odakantikañca jaṅgale bhūmibhāge yāva idāni udakaṃ āgamissatīti, tāva khato āvāṭo viya. "
