538721,116,1034,131,152,1,132,16,"Etadatthañhi so nidheti‘‘ atthāvahe kismiñcideva karaṇīye samuppanne atthāya me bhavissati, tassa me kiccassa nipphattiyā bhavissatī’’ ti. "
538722,116,1034,153,160,1,62,7,Kiccanipphattiyeva hi tassa kicce samuppanne atthoti veditabbo. 
538723,116,1035,2,2,1,18,1,Dutiyagāthāvaṇṇanā 
538724,116,1036,2,11,1,103,8,Evaṃ nidhānappayojanaṃ dassento atthādhigamādhippāyaṃ dassetvā idāni anatthāpagamādhippāyaṃ dassetumāha– 
538725,116,1037,2,15,1,40,6,"2.‘‘ Rājato vā duruttassa, corato pīḷitassa vā. "
538726,116,1038,2,12,1,45,7,"Iṇassa vā pamokkhāya, dubbhikkhe āpadāsu vā’’ ti. "
538727,116,1039,2,29,1,152,19,Tassattho ‘‘ atthāya me bhavissatī’’ ti ca‘‘ iṇassa vā pamokkhāyā’’ ti ca ettha vuttehi dvīhi bhavissatipamokkhāya-padehi saddhiṃ yathāsambhavaṃ yojetvā veditabbo. 
538728,116,1040,2,72,1,368,50,"Tatthāyaṃ yojanā– na kevalaṃ atthāya me bhavissatīti eva puriso nidhiṃ nidheti, kintu‘‘ ayaṃ coro’’ ti vā‘‘ pāradāriko’’ ti vā‘‘ suṅkaghātako’’ ti vā evamādinā nayena paccatthikehi paccāmittehi duruttassa me sato rājato vā pamokkhāya bhavissati, sandhicchedādīhi dhanaharaṇena vā,‘‘ ettakaṃ hiraññasuvaṇṇaṃ dehī’’ ti jīvaggāhena vā corehi me pīḷitassa sato corato vā pamokkhāya bhavissati. "
538729,116,1040,73,95,1,101,16,"Santi me iṇāyikā, te maṃ‘‘ iṇaṃ dehī’’ ti codessanti, tehi me codiyamānassa iṇassa vā pamokkhāya bhavissati. "
538730,116,1040,96,119,1,143,19,"Hoti so samayo, yaṃ dubbhikkhaṃ hoti dussassaṃ dullabhapiṇḍaṃ, tattha na sukaraṃ appadhanena yāpetuṃ, tathāvidhe āgate dubbhikkhe vā me bhavissati . "
538731,116,1040,120,139,1,140,18,"Yathārūpā āpadā uppajjanti aggito vā udakato vā appiyadāyādato vā, tathārūpāsu vā uppannāsu āpadāsu me bhavissatītipi puriso nidhiṃ nidhetīti. "
538732,116,1041,2,16,1,149,14,Evaṃ atthādhigamādhippāyaṃ anatthāpagamādhippāyañcāti dvīhi gāthāhi duvidhaṃ nidhānappayojanaṃ dassetvā idāni tameva duvidhaṃ payojanaṃ nigamento āha–
538733,116,1042,2,13,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Etadatthāya lokasmiṃ, nidhi nāma nidhīyatī’’ ti. "
538734,116,1043,2,28,1,119,17,Tassattho – yvāyaṃ‘‘ atthāya me bhavissatī’’ ti ca‘‘ rājato vā duruttassā’’ ti evamādīhi ca atthādhigamo anatthāpagamo ca dassito. 
