538965,116,1145,43,47,1,19,4,Atha te bhikkhū āha–
538966,116,1145,48,84,1,220,25,"‘‘ na, bhikkhave, tumhākaṃ aññaṃ sappāyasenāsanaṃ atthi, tattheva tumhe viharantā āsavakkhayaṃ pāpuṇissatha, gacchatha, bhikkhave, tameva senāsanaṃ upanissāya viharatha, sace pana devatāhi abhayaṃ icchatha, imaṃ parittaṃ uggaṇhatha. "
