538976,116,1148,2,2,1,19,1,Paṭhamagāthāvaṇṇanā 
538977,116,1149,2,20,1,107,11,1. Idāni‘‘ assa karissāmatthavaṇṇanan’’ ti vuttattā evaṃ katanidānasodhanassa assa suttassa atthavaṇṇanā ārabbhate. 
538978,116,1149,21,36,1,117,12,"Tattha {karaṇīyamatthakusalenā}ti imissā paṭhamagāthāya tāva ayaṃ padavaṇṇanā– karaṇīyan ti kātabbaṃ, karaṇārahanti attho. "
538979,116,1149,37,56,1,108,15,"{Attho}ti paṭipadā, yaṃ vā kiñci attano hitaṃ, taṃ sabbaṃ araṇīyato atthoti vuccati, araṇīyato nāma upagantabbato. "
538980,116,1149,57,63,1,55,6,Atthe kusalena atthakusalena atthachekenāti vuttaṃ hoti. 
538981,116,1149,64,67,1,25,3,Yan ti aniyamitapaccattaṃ. 
538982,116,1149,68,77,1,60,8,"Nti niyamitaupayogaṃ, ubhayampi vā yaṃ tan ti paccattavacanaṃ. "
538983,116,1149,78,92,1,98,11,"Santaṃ padan ti upayogavacanaṃ, tattha lakkhaṇato santaṃ, pattabbato padaṃ, nibbānassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
538984,116,1149,93,96,1,28,2,{Abhisameccā}ti abhisamāgantvā. 
