538993,116,1150,22,27,1,40,4,Tattha saṅkhepato sikkhattayaṃ karaṇīyaṃ. 
538994,116,1150,28,37,1,72,6,"Sīlavipatti, diṭṭhivipatti, ācāravipatti, ājīvavipattīti evamādi akaraṇīyaṃ. "
538995,116,1150,38,44,1,43,5,"Tathā atthi atthakusalo, atthi anatthakusalo. "
538996,116,1150,45,63,1,126,16,"Tattha yo imasmiṃ sāsane pabbajitvā na attānaṃ sammā payojeti, khaṇḍasīlo hoti, ekavīsatividhaṃ anesanaṃ nissāya jīvikaṃ kappeti. "
538997,116,1150,64,88,1,291,22,Seyyathidaṃ– veḷudānaṃ pattadānaṃ pupphadānaṃ phaladānaṃ dantakaṭṭhadānaṃ mukhodakadānaṃ sinānadānaṃ cuṇṇadānaṃ mattikādānaṃ cāṭukamyataṃ muggasūpyataṃ pāribhaṭayataṃ jaṅghapesanikaṃ vejjakammaṃ dūtakammaṃ pahiṇagamanaṃ piṇḍapaṭipiṇḍaṃ dānānuppadānaṃ vatthuvijjaṃ nakkhattavijjaṃ aṅgavijjanti. 
538998,116,1150,89,93,1,27,4,Chabbidhe ca agocare carati. 
538999,116,1150,94,98,1,78,3,Seyyathidaṃ– vesiyāgocare vidhavathullakumārikapaṇḍakabhikkhunīpānāgāragocareti. 
539000,116,1150,99,131,1,302,28,"Saṃsaṭṭho ca viharati rājūhi rājamahāmattehi titthiyehi titthiyasāvakehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena, yāni vā pana tāni kulāni assaddhāni appasannāni anopānabhūtāni akkosakaparibhāsakāni anatthakāmāni ahitaaphāsukayogakkhemakāmāni bhikkhūnaṃ… pe… upāsikānaṃ, tathārūpāni kulāni sevati bhajati payirupāsati. "
539001,116,1150,132,134,1,18,2,Ayaṃ anatthakusalo. 
539002,116,1151,2,25,1,233,21,"Yo pana imasmiṃ sāsane pabbajitvā attānaṃ sammā payojeti, anesanaṃ pahāya catupārisuddhisīle patiṭṭhātukāmo saddhāsīsena pātimokkhasaṃvaraṃ satisīsena indriyasaṃvaraṃ vīriyasīsena ājīvapārisuddhiṃ, paññāsīsena paccayapaṭisevanaṃ pūreti. "
539003,116,1151,26,28,1,16,2,Ayaṃ atthakusalo. 
539004,116,1152,2,25,1,360,19,"Yo vā sattāpattikkhandhasodhanavasena pātimokkhasaṃvaraṃ, chadvāre ghaṭṭitārammaṇesu abhijjhādīnaṃ anuppattivasena indrisaṃvaraṃ, anesanaparivajjanavasena viññuppasatthabuddhabuddhasāvakavaṇṇitapaccayapaṭisevanena ca ājīvapārisuddhiṃ, yathāvuttapaccavekkhaṇavasena paccayapaṭisevanaṃ, catuiriyāpathaparivattane sātthakatādipaccavekkhaṇavasena sampajaññañca sodheti. "
539005,116,1152,26,28,1,18,2,Ayampi atthakusalo. 
539006,116,1153,2,29,1,198,24,"Yo vā yathā ūsodakaṃ paṭicca saṃkiliṭṭhaṃ vatthaṃ pariyodāpayati, chārikaṃ paṭicca ādāso, ukkāmukhaṃ paṭicca jātarūpaṃ, tathā ñāṇaṃ paṭicca sīlaṃ vodāyatīti ñatvā ñāṇodakena dhovanto sīlaṃ pariyodāpeti. "
539007,116,1153,30,67,1,238,30,"Yathā ca kikī sakuṇikā aṇḍaṃ, camarī migo vāladhiṃ, ekaputtikā nārī piyaṃ ekaputtakaṃ, ekanayano puriso taṃ ekanayanañca rakkhati, tathā ativiya appamatto attano sīlakkhandhaṃ rakkhati, sāyaṃ pātaṃ paccavekkhamāno aṇumattampi vajjaṃ na passati. "
539008,116,1153,68,70,1,18,2,Ayampi atthakusalo. 
539009,116,1154,2,21,1,168,16,"Yo vā pana avippaṭisārakare sīle patiṭṭhāya kilesavikkhambhanapaṭipadaṃ paggaṇhāti, taṃ paggaṇhitvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ karoti, kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā samāpattiyo nibbatteti. "
539010,116,1154,22,24,1,18,2,Ayampi atthakusalo. 
539011,116,1155,2,15,1,95,12,"Yo vā pana samāpattito vuṭṭhāya saṅkhāre sammasitvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇāti, ayaṃ atthakusalānaṃ aggo. "
539012,116,1155,16,35,1,162,17,"Tattha ye ime yāva avippaṭisārakare sīle patiṭṭhānena yāva vā kilesavikkhambhanapaṭipadāyapaggahaṇena vaṇṇitā atthakusalā, te imasmiṃ atthe {atthakusalā}ti adhippetā. "
539013,116,1155,36,41,1,25,5,Tathā vidhā ca te bhikkhū. 
539014,116,1155,42,56,1,93,10,Tena bhagavā te bhikkhū sandhāya ekapuggalādhiṭṭhānāya desanāya‘‘ karaṇīyamatthakusalenā’’ ti āha. 
539015,116,1156,2,22,1,83,12,Tato ‘‘ kiṃ karaṇīyan’’ ti tesaṃ sañjātakaṅkhānaṃ āha‘‘ yantaṃ santaṃ padaṃ abhisameccā’’ ti. 
539016,116,1156,23,36,1,128,12,Ayamettha adhippāyo– taṃ buddhānubuddhehi vaṇṇitaṃ santaṃ nibbānapadaṃ paṭivedhavasena abhisamecca viharitukāmena yaṃ karaṇīyanti. 
539017,116,1156,37,53,1,116,15,"Ettha ca yan ti imassa gāthāpadassa ādito vuttameva karaṇīyanti adhikārato anuvattati, taṃ santaṃ padaṃ abhisameccāti. "
539018,116,1156,54,64,1,78,9,"Ayaṃ pana yasmā sāvasesapāṭho attho, tasmā viharitukāmenāti vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
539019,116,1157,2,30,1,215,22,"Atha vā santaṃ padaṃ {abhisameccā}ti anussavādivasena lokiyapaññāya nibbānapadaṃ‘‘ santan’’ ti ñatvā taṃ adhigantukāmena yantaṃ karaṇīyanti adhikārato anuvattati, taṃ karaṇīyamatthakusalenāti evampettha adhippāyo veditabbo. "
539020,116,1157,31,57,1,97,14,Atha vā‘‘ karaṇīyamatthakusalenā’’ ti vutte‘‘ kin’’ ti cintentānaṃ āha‘‘ yantaṃ santaṃ padaṃ abhisameccā’’ ti. 
539021,116,1157,58,77,1,137,16,"Tassevaṃ adhippāyo veditabbo– lokiyapaññāya santaṃ padaṃ abhisamecca yaṃ karaṇīyaṃ kātabbaṃ, taṃ karaṇīyaṃ, karaṇārahameva tanti vuttaṃ hoti. "
539022,116,1158,2,6,1,14,3,Kiṃ pana tanti ? 
539023,116,1158,7,17,1,106,9,"Kimaññaṃ siyā aññatra tadadhigamupāyato, kāmañcetaṃ karaṇārahaṭṭhena sikkhattayadīpakena ādipadeneva vuttaṃ. "
539024,116,1158,18,30,1,72,9,"Tathā hi tassa atthavaṇṇanāyaṃ avocumhā‘‘ atthi karaṇīyaṃ, atthi akaraṇīyaṃ. "
