539026,116,1158,40,51,1,80,10,"Atisaṅkhepena desitattā pana tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kehici viññātaṃ, kehici na viññātaṃ. "
539027,116,1158,52,85,1,182,26,"Tato yehi na viññātaṃ, tesaṃ viññāpanatthaṃ yaṃ visesato āraññakena bhikkhunā kātabbaṃ, taṃ vitthārento‘‘ sakko ujū ca suhujū ca, suvaco cassa mudu anatimānī’’ ti imaṃ tāva upaḍḍhagāthamāha. "
539028,116,1159,2,6,1,15,3,Kiṃ vuttaṃ hoti? 
539029,116,1159,7,53,1,423,43,"Santaṃ padaṃ abhisamecca viharitukāmo, lokiyapaññāya vā taṃ abhisamecca tadadhigamāya paṭipajjamāno āraññako bhikkhu dutiyacatutthapadhāniyaṅgasamannāgamena kāye ca jīvite ca anapekkho hutvā saccappaṭivedhāya paṭipajjituṃ sakko assa, tathā kasiṇaparikammavattasamādānādīsu attano pattacīvarappaṭisaṅkharaṇādīsu ca yāni tāni sabrahmacārīnaṃ uccāvacāni kiṃ karaṇīyāni, tesu aññesu ca evarūpesu sakko assa dakkho analaso samattho. "
539030,116,1159,54,60,1,57,6,Sakko hontopi ca tatiyapadhāniyaṅgasamannāgamena uju assa. 
539031,116,1159,61,77,1,136,16,Uju hontopi ca sakiṃ ujubhāvena daharakāle vā ujubhāvena santosaṃ anāpajjitvā yāvajīvaṃ punappunaṃ asithilakaraṇena suṭṭhutaraṃ uju assa. 
539032,116,1159,78,84,1,36,5,"Asaṭhatāya vā uju, amāyāvitāya suhuju. "
539033,116,1159,85,91,1,55,5,"Kāyavacīvaṅkappahānena vā uju, manovaṅkappahānena suhuju. "
539034,116,1159,92,102,1,89,9,"Asantaguṇassa vā anāvikaraṇena uju, asantaguṇena uppannassa lābhassa anadhivāsanena suhuju. "
539035,116,1159,103,113,1,103,10,Evaṃ ārammaṇalakkhaṇūpanijjhānehi purimadvayatatiyasikkhāhi payogāsayasuddhīhi ca uju ca suhuju ca assa. 
539036,116,1160,2,14,1,55,11,"Na kevalañca uju ca suhuju ca, apica pana suvaco ca assa. "
539037,116,1160,15,68,1,235,39,"Yo hi puggalo‘‘ idaṃ na kattabban’’ ti vutto‘‘ kiṃ te diṭṭhaṃ, kiṃ te sutaṃ, ko me sutvā vadasi, kiṃ upajjhāyo ācariyo sandiṭṭho sambhatto vā’’ ti vadeti, tuṇhībhāvena vā taṃ viheseti, sampaṭicchitvā vā na tathā karoti, so visesādhigamassa dūre hoti. "
539038,116,1160,69,113,1,248,33,"Yo pana ovadiyamāno‘‘ sādhu, bhante suṭṭhu vuttaṃ, attano vajjaṃ nāma duddasaṃ hoti, punapi maṃ evarūpaṃ disvā vadeyyātha anukampaṃ upādāya, cirassaṃ me tumhākaṃ santikā ovādo laddho’’ ti vadati, yathānusiṭṭhañca paṭipajjati, so visesādhigamassa avidūre hoti. "
539039,116,1160,114,123,1,64,9,Tasmā evaṃ parassa vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā karonto suvaco ca assa. 
539040,116,1161,2,10,1,30,6,"Yathā ca suvaco, evaṃ mudu assa. "
539041,116,1161,11,31,1,203,19,{Mudū}ti gahaṭṭhehi dūtagamanapahiṇagamanādīsu niyujjamāno tattha mudubhāvaṃ akatvā thaddho hutvā vattapaṭipattiyaṃ sakalabrahmacariye ca mudu assa suparikammakatasuvaṇṇaṃ viya tattha tattha viniyogakkhamo. 
539042,116,1161,32,43,1,101,11,Atha vā mudūti abhākuṭiko uttānamukho sukhasambhāso paṭisanthāravutti sutitthaṃ viya sukhāvagāho assa. 
539043,116,1161,44,63,1,153,16,"Na kevalañca mudu, apica pana anatimānī assa, jātigottādīhi atimānavatthūhi pare nātimaññeyya, sāriputtatthero viya caṇḍālakumārakasamena cetasā vihareyyāti. "
539044,116,1162,2,2,1,18,1,Dutiyagāthāvaṇṇanā 
539045,116,1163,2,32,1,202,22,2. Evaṃ bhagavā santaṃ padaṃ abhisamecca viharitukāmassa tadadhigamāya vā paṭipajjamānassa visesato āraññakassa bhikkhuno ekaccaṃ karaṇīyaṃ vatvā puna tatuttaripi vattukāmo‘‘ santussako cā’’ ti dutiyagāthamāha. 
539046,116,1164,2,17,1,103,11,Tattha ‘‘ santuṭṭhī ca kataññutā’’ ti ettha vuttappabhedena dvādasavidhena santosena santussatīti santussako. 
539047,116,1164,18,32,1,84,11,"Atha vā tussatīti tussako, sakena tussako, santena tussako, samena tussakoti santussako. "
539048,116,1164,33,75,1,275,33,"Tattha sakaṃ nāma‘‘ piṇḍiyālopabhojanaṃ nissāyā’’ ti evaṃ upasampadamaṇḍale uddiṭṭhaṃ attanā ca sampaṭicchitaṃ catupaccayajātaṃ, tena sundarena vā asundarena vā sakkaccaṃ vā asakkaccaṃ vā dinnena paṭiggahaṇakāle paribhogakāle ca vikāraṃ adassetvā yāpento‘‘ sakena tussako’’ ti vuccati. "
539049,116,1164,76,103,1,143,20,"Santaṃ nāma yaṃ laddhaṃ hoti attano‘ vijjamānaṃ , tena santeneva tussanto tato paraṃ na patthento atricchataṃ pajahanto‘‘ santena tussako’’ ti vuccati. "
539050,116,1164,104,121,1,109,12,"Samaṃ nāma iṭṭhāniṭṭhesu anunayapaṭighappahānaṃ, tena samena sabbārammaṇesu tussanto‘‘ samena tussako’’ ti vuccati. "
539051,116,1165,2,9,1,48,6,"Sukhena bharīyatīti subharo, suposoti vuttaṃ hoti. "
539052,116,1165,10,42,1,218,26,"Yo hi bhikkhu manussehi sālimaṃsodanādīnaṃ patte pūretvā dinnepi dummukhabhāvaṃ anattamanabhāvameva ca dasseti, tesaṃ vā sammukhāva taṃ piṇḍapātaṃ‘‘ kiṃ tumhehi dinnan’’ ti apasādento sāmaṇeragahaṭṭhādīnaṃ deti, esa dubbharo. "
539053,116,1165,43,59,1,77,11,Etaṃ disvā manussā dūratova parivajjenti‘‘ dubbharo bhikkhu na sakkā posetun’’ ti . 
539054,116,1165,60,80,1,115,19,"Yo pana yaṃ kiñci lūkhaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā appaṃ vā bahuṃ vā labhitvā attamano vippasannamukho hutvā yāpeti, esa subharo. "
539055,116,1165,81,106,1,139,18,"Etaṃ disvā manussā ativiya vissatthā honti,‘‘ amhākaṃ bhadanto subharo, thokathokenāpi tussati, mayameva naṃ posessāmā’’ ti paṭiññaṃ katvā posenti. "
539056,116,1165,107,111,1,32,4,Evarūpo idha subharoti adhippeto. 
