539236,117,9,37,112,1,488,55,"Satthā dhammasabhaṃ āgantvā alaṅkatabuddhāsane nisīditvā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ oloketvā bhikkhuādīsu pana ye ārabbha dhammakathā samuṭṭhāti, tehi saddhiṃ tathāgatā sallapanti, tasmā ajja upāsake ārabbha pubbacariyappaṭisaṃyuttā dhammakathā samuṭṭhahissatīti ñatvā upāsakehi saddhiṃ sallapanto‘‘ uposathikattha, upāsakā’’ ti upāsake pucchitvā‘‘ āma, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ sādhu, upāsakā, kalyāṇaṃ vo kataṃ, apica anacchariyaṃ kho panetaṃ, yaṃ tumhe mādisaṃ buddhaṃ ovādadāyakaṃ ācariyaṃ labhantā uposathaṃ kareyyātha. "
