539238,117,10,2,48,1,251,35,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatto nāma rājā rajjaṃ kārento puttassa uparajjaṃ datvā tassa mahantaṃ yasaṃ disvā‘‘ rajjampi me gaṇheyyā’’ ti uppannāsaṅko‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ ito nikkhamitvā yattha te ruccati, tattha vasitvā mama accayena kulasantakaṃ rajjaṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti āha. "
539239,117,10,49,74,1,176,21,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā pitaraṃ vanditvā nikkhamitvā anupubbena yamunaṃ gantvā yamunāya ca samuddassa ca pabbatassa ca antare paṇṇasālaṃ māpetvā vanamūlaphalāhāro paṭivasati. 
539240,117,10,75,100,1,235,25,Tadā samuddassa heṭṭhime nāgabhavane ekā matapatikā nāgamāṇavikā aññāsaṃ sapatikānaṃ yasaṃ oloketvā kilesaṃ nissāya nāgabhavanā nikkhamitvā samuddatīre vicarantī rājaputtassa padavalañjaṃ disvā padānusārena gantvā taṃ paṇṇasālaṃ addasa. 
539241,117,10,101,106,1,41,5,Tadā rājaputto phalāphalatthāya gato hoti. 
539242,117,10,107,144,1,253,30,"Sā paṇṇasālaṃ pavisitvā kaṭṭhattharaṇañceva sesaparikkhāre ca disvā cintesi‘‘ idaṃ ekassa pabbajitassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ, vīmaṃsissāmi naṃ‘ saddhāya pabbajito nu kho no’ ti, sace hi saddhāya pabbajito bhavissati nekkhammādhimutto, na me alaṅkatasayanaṃ sādiyissati. "
539243,117,10,145,155,1,79,8,"Sace kāmābhirato bhavissati, na saddhāpabbajito, mama sayanasmiṃyeva nipajjissati. "
539244,117,10,156,167,1,57,9,Atha naṃ gahetvā attano sāmikaṃ katvā idheva vasissāmī’’ ti. 
539245,117,10,168,187,1,193,19,Sā nāgabhavanaṃ gantvā dibbapupphāni ceva dibbagandhe ca āharitvā dibbapupphasayanaṃ sajjetvā paṇṇasālāyaṃ pupphūpahāraṃ katvā gandhacuṇṇaṃ vikiritvā paṇṇasālaṃ alaṅkaritvā nāgabhavanameva gatā. 
539246,117,11,2,53,1,371,41,"Rājaputto sāyanhasamayaṃ āgantvā paṇṇasālaṃ paviṭṭho taṃ pavattiṃ disvā‘‘ kena nu kho imaṃ sayanaṃ sajjitan’’ ti phalāphalaṃ paribhuñjitvā‘‘ aho sugandhāni pupphāni, manāpaṃ vata katvā sayanaṃ paññattan’’ ti na saddhāpabbajitabhāvena somanassajāto pupphasayane parivattitvā nipanno niddaṃ okkamitvā punadivase sūriyuggamane uṭṭhāya paṇṇasālaṃ asammajjitvā phalāphalatthāya agamāsi. "
539247,117,11,54,92,1,277,31,"Nāgamāṇavikā tasmiṃ khaṇe āgantvā milātāni pupphāni disvā‘‘ kāmādhimutto esa, na saddhāpabbajito, sakkā naṃ gaṇhitun’’ ti ñatvā purāṇapupphāni nīharitvā aññāni pupphāni āharitvā tatheva navapupphasayanaṃ sajjetvā paṇṇasālaṃ alaṅkaritvā caṅkame pupphāni vikiritvā nāgabhavanameva gatā. "
539248,117,11,93,112,1,96,14,So taṃ divasampi pupphasayane sayitvā punadivase cintesi‘‘ ko nu kho imaṃ paṇṇasālaṃ alaṅkarotī’’ ti? 
539249,117,11,113,120,1,67,7,So phalāphalatthāya agantvā paṇṇasālato avidūre paṭicchanno aṭṭhāsi. 
